      <title>帕内塔称欧洲央行现在降息可避免日后“迟缓而仓促”的行动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/panetta-says-ecb-cuts-now-avoid-tardy-and-hasty-action-later</link>
